---
title: Golden Chicken & Mujadara Rice Bowl with Lemony Greens, Zesty Yoghurt & Roasted Almonds
description: This dish is a true feast for champions! Juicy Middle-Eastern spiced chicken, lemony sauteed veg and zingy yoghurt sit
atop a new favourite, Mujadara rice, with lentils and caramelised onion stirred through. Here’s a bowl of wholesome
goodness that packs a punch with flavour.
